Product Description

This wallet has oodles of style and makes for a good travelling companion. With a trendy textured look this wallet comes with a chain sling and has many pockets to store your all-important credit and business cards. There is a distinct emblazoned 'H' on the flap giving this wallet a classy look. Sling it on with a fitted dress with pumps for a night out.
